rcumstances. S&iacute; TV disclaims any and all liability for any damages caused by theft or disclosure of your User ID. Do not disclose or authorize anyone else to use your User ID. You agree to immediately notify us if you become aware of or believe there is or may have been any unauthorized use of your User ID or any other need to cancel your User ID for security reasons.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><b>4. MODIFICATIONS</b> <br />\r\nS&iacute; TV retains the right to change the terms of this Agreement at any time in its sole discretion. We will post or display notices of material changes on the S&iacute; TV website. Once posted, such changes become effective immediately, and if you use the S&iacute; TV website after they become effective, you thereby agree to be bound by the changes. You should check back frequently and review this Agreement regularly so you are aware of the most current rights and obligations that apply to you. S&iacute; TV retains the right to change, modify, withdraw, suspend or even permanently discontinue all or any portions of the S&iacute; TV website at any time, without any liability or obligation to you, with or without notice.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><b>5. PRIVACY</b> <br />\r\nWe respect your privacy and the use and protection of your Personal Information. Please see our S&iacute; TV Privacy Policy for important information and disclosures relating to the collection and use of your Personal Information in connection with your use of the S&iacute; TV website. If you have any questions regarding S&iacute; TV\'s privacy practices, you may send your question to us by e-mail to <a href=\"mailto:feedback@sitv.com\">feedback@sitv.com</a> or by U.S. mail to S&iacute; TV, Inc., Attn: Webmaster, 3030 Andrita Street, Los Angeles, California 90065.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><b>6. USE OF MATERIAL </b><br />\r\nThe S&iacute; TV website, including but not limited to all content, show information, media and materials, website code, design, text, ima