INSERT INTO `node_revisions` VALUES ('213','215','1','Help','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">How do I register for the site?</p>\r\n<p>On the upper right hand corner of the site you will see a button to register. This will bring you to the register page. This is where you will create username, provide an email, and fill out your personal and profile information. Once you click &ldquo;submit&rdquo; you will receive an email from the Network supplying you with a default password and link. You can click on the link and insert your default password. You will then be able to change the default password to the password of your choice. After you&rsquo;ve done it all, you will be a new member of our [S&iacute;] Community!</p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">I love S&iacute; TV. How can I contribute?</p>\r\n<p>You can contact us by visiting our Contact page located on the bottom of the site. Just fill out the form and tell us about yourself and how you would like to contribute.</p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">Can I contribute if I am not Latino?</p>\r\n<p>Of course! Our community is just that &ndash; a community. We are Latino-driven but understand that everyone influences our lives. Our site is a reflection of those influences. </p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">How can I get S&iacute; TV on my TV?</p>\r\n<p>Just click the &ldquo;Get S&iacute; TV&rdquo; button and follow the steps. If you do not have access in your area call your cable provider and ask for S&iacute; TV to be put on their roster of channels. </p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">Can I watch full episodes of my favorite S&iacute; TV shows?</p>\r\n<p>You can see clips of our different shows right now. We are currently working on getting full-episodes of all your favorite S&iacute; TV shows up online so you can watch them at anytime, day or night. In the meantime, contact us and let us know which shows you&rsquo;d like to see available first.</p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">How do I get my own blog?</p>\r\n<p>If you are interested in blogging, create a profile </p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">I\'m a journalist and I want to talk to someone at S&iacute; TV. Who can I contact?</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your inquiry. Please call us at (866) 748-8463, or contact Brenda Bedolla at <a href=\"\">bbedolla@sitv.com.</a>  </p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">How do I change my default picture?</p>\r\n<p>* Select &ldquo;view profile&rdquo; in the upper right hand corner of the site<br />\r\n* Once inside of your profile select the edit tab<br />\r\n* Here is where you can choose to edit account information, personal information, profile information, and add your user image.<br />\r\n* When finished select the save button at the bottom.<br />\r\n* Note: You can only have one profile image up at a time. If you want to change your profile image, check the &ldquo;delete&rdquo; option below the image. Then you can either save or upload a new photo which will automatically replace the old one</p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">I\'m trying to upload an image and I am getting an error message. What is wrong?</p>\r\n<p>* Make sure the image you are trying to upload is in one of the formats [S&iacute;] accepts (.gif, .jpg).<br />\r\n* Make sure the filename is simple and short, with no spaces or funny characters. &quot;Image.jpg&quot; is a good filename &quot;Me at the beach! Drinking some beers~~.jpg&quot; is probably not going to work.<br />\r\n* Make sure the file is less than 2MB. We do not allow images over 2MB.</p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">How do I change my email address and/or password?</p>\r\n<p>* Select &ldquo;edit profile&rdquo; in the upper right hand corner of the site<br />\r\n* Once inside your profile select the edit tab<br />\r\n* Here is where you can choose to edit account information, personal information, profile information and add your user image<br />\r\n* When finished select the save button at the bottom<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">For any other questions or concerns, please email <a href=\"\">websupport@sitv.com</a>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>','<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"question-cap\">How do I register for the site?</p>','','1260391986','2');
